    static class BoundedMinHeapUnsynchronized.BoundedMinHeapIterator
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Iterator
    auxiliary nested class to provide an java.util.Iterator interface for traversing this min-heap (in order). This iterator is very expensive (makes a full copy of the underlying array) and should not be used unless really needed.
